publisher			Timbre Interactive							
publish_time	 2015年8月12日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Sentris is a musical performance game. Make your own music as you Drop, Recycle, and Stack "Sound Blocks" into a spinning loop. Freestyle with a huge degree of musical control. Or focus on achieving the goal and let your song emerge organically.* Experimental music-based gameplay that enables personal expression and creativity* Deceptively simple, challenging, and deep* Play and Remix 20 levels with 12 musical voices, 12 key signatures, 7 musical modes, and up to 400 beats per minute* Freestyle to perform the game like a musical instrument* Export your loops to .wav and use them in other music/audio software* Endless mode with infinite musical emergence						
title	 Sentris			
